Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:58.50,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(595,80)\fad(2000,800)}燃放超大焰火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:40.03,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(500,0)}秋之暴風來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:23.19,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}過ぎるだけの時間が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.72,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:32.11,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}ここにいると心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.45,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:41.36,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}迷いながら涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:47.44,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}不器用だね夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:53.48,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}大空を見上げなにも言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:22:01.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}胸が痛む訳 考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}Days of Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:06.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}風を走り抜けて‥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:09.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}君と僕の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:12.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:18.00,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}きらきら光る太陽が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:22.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:28.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,500)}永遠など知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:23.19,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}後悔著那些庸碌虛度的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.72,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}一定要鐫刻下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:32.11,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}心靈在此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:41.36,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}迷茫著嚥下淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:47.44,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}真沒用啊  連夢想都離我也遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:53.48,OPCN3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}抬頭望著天空  什麼也說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:22:01.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}心中一直思考著胸口泛起痛楚的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:06.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}奔跑著穿越風阻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:09.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}你和我之間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:12.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}有什麼正在展開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:18.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}閃著耀眼光芒的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:22.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}朝著照耀的地方一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:28.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,500)}雖然我不明白永遠為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田同學有你的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兩封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山同學…你之前都戴隱形眼鏡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！ 一個疏忽竟然就這副樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田同學不要看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼就對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡娘七海同學也好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…快住手學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}大家都是女孩子有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  那封信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8\fs18}（「來做遊戲吧！」選拔委員）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}不可以啦  男生們都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就去房間裏繼續？還是說去浴室裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪都不去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去外面干吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生可是需要很多驚喜的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No surprise no life哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通過初審了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我31日去發表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好七海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好啦  空太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:00:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼另一封是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（教我戀愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道  戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人果然是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是生活在河川或是小池中淡水魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}（日語中「鯉」和「戀愛」的發音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀賞用的錦鯉價格依據花色來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴的似乎要賣到幾百萬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此你個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道的難道是魚的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我變得心動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說得這麼淡然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我心頭一緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可無法擔此重任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多少也燃起點鬥志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來為什麼會突然想到戀愛什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是綾乃對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要描繪真實的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的方法就是去戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說誰都能在人生中描繪出一個戀愛的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧那個編輯…能這麼淡定地講出這麼不害臊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,31日有個決定新連載的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,31日？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊抱歉  那天我有個發表會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發表會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「來做遊戲吧！」的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為通過的初審所以得好好準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是同一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不穿褲子跑進男生的房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生都是H的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我當做男生的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦  他還沒有教我戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛你也看到了吧  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名的編輯這麼對她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也不能保證就不會犯下什麼錯誤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我是禽獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君也要為發表會做準備不能打擾他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有打擾他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嘛…雖然是沒有打擾到啦但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有打擾到我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒關繫了但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要糾纏在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又沒打算要糾纏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和學弟君糾纏在一起的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為布丁是飲料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少請先統一話題再講
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  所以說搖搖布丁是邪道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}（摇摇布丁  プリンシェイク是Pokka Corporation推出的一款饮料  饮用前先要摇晃罐子）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海知道戀愛是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs16}（二次審查  企劃書發表的介紹）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.52,SPEC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,78)}[ 空太先生登陸了 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:27.52,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,111)}赤阪  現在有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介大人現在正在認真考察
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果從兩邊同時打開左右均可開門的冰箱會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那女僕醬也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於參加企劃發表會有什麼建議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}對於對話中使用了「那麼」「也可以」這種誰都可以的字眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}空太大人我應該用什麼方式來殺掉你懲罰呢（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(375,330)\fs18}給予
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}（「給予」和「殺掉」同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明都已經有結果了(((((;°Д°)))))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.05,SPEC3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(127,280)}穿西裝，就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼突然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.26,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(125,270)}還有就是找櫻花莊的人來進行練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.26,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(125,270)}湊巧的是我們這裏聚集的都是些很有個性的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.01,SPEC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(290,272)}[ 龍之介下線了 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行篇開幕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16\fad(200,0)}（學弟君  修行篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…根據這樣的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…不是讓核心玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是為了讓大多數玩家都能樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20分53秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是根據網上藤澤和希得獎時的企劃書進行參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話過程中的起承轉合請說得明白一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得這不是平時的學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬語也處處都好怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種要素都說得太詳細了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最關鍵的地方卻變得讓人無法理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我再修改一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海說幹得好的話就給你親親哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有說過！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是臉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是部位的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,概念簡單又有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  簡單又靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是爽快感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  你在別人的房間裏做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在設計角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼要在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得只要在這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能明白什麼是戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被青山發現的話她會生氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太張口閉口都是七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  太陽升了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發表會的原稿的修改聽取了大家的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地修改不停地練習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在重複了十次以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迎來了決戰的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天去求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和誰去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查了一下又問了路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  明明你今天也要決定是否連載了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  神田空太先生  請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤澤和希…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在開始企劃說明之前我能問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為如何才能成為一個遊戲創作人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定得回答點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呢…那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了…腦中一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這不是神田家的小子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一身是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說嘛  當然是約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…怎麼了啊小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田空太先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常遺憾  您無緣本次的企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連載的事情怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從11月號開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  那麼必須得畫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要待在這裏  快去畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在先走開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏可不是前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  是遺憾獎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  絕不會那麼簡單就成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太肯定也有了覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很在意嗎  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  來辦青山的歡迎會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  贊成  真不愧是仁  這個點子太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}等等啊  為什麼會變這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據這個發展  只剩今天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定好了就開始做吧  我有個一直準備好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到6點  全員集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（「來做遊戲吧！」一審通過的通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（寶箱）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全人類所期待的約定之日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  學弟君覺得哪個比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了  是泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼對內衣和泳衣的反應那麼不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個謎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別往深處想了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你往別人家裏塞了那麼多泳衣究竟想要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舉辦七海的游泳歡迎大會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  一起去吧  學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和七海和真白和我的泳裝形象正在等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要把自己說兩次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說了這個時間還有游泳館開門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  難道說你要偷偷潛入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經和千尋說過了  所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歡迎會什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的正好  青山也挑個喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然的話  我幫你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舉辦七海的游泳歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海你要穿哪個？  學弟君說這個就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——神田君？ ——我才沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞錯戰鬥對象啊  敵人是這個宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要繫帶的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——三鷹學長！ ——仁學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可從來沒說過我要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快點把這些收拾好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  去嘛去嘛  七海  學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  再說明天學校就要開學了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就是這個  不穿泳衣的話暑假是不會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧？  對啊  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  青山游泳歡迎大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海在召喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一下準備運動會比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山和椎名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也快換好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有問三鷹學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  什麼都別說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  和上井草學姐穿的那種大膽的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  這我也已經是很盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次穿這種泳衣  要是很奇怪的話該怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  真的很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說話又帶關西腔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都稱讚七海了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招  水泳板飛刃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  青山  一起跑起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必殺！  鑽石噴涌嘩啦嘩啦大瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  稍微試射一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！  要擋的話就擋住自己的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  解不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是學弟君的泳褲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}還給我  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太倒霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳大會什麼的果然要走光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No 走光 no life啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}你們特地把這個帶來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學弟君也來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}櫻花莊的歡迎會火鍋是不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們在這裏做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹學長不是說得到許可了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種許可學校怎麼可能會給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  藏哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾出來  你這偷泳池的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吧唧吧唧  吧唧吧唧的  玩得那麼歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別撓啊  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要向上看  絕對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  不要動  椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比以前的那個刺繡更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,125,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}（安產祈願）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你會很消沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停滯不前可不行哦  空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  那個大叔的臉好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這群混蛋  是櫻花莊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏肆意揮霍青春  我絕不放過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  感覺變得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是青山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  人家難得關心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕啊  認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來是聽到椎名說連載決定下來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺像是自己被否定了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心都要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以無法逃避躲藏後悔和懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才更簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有接著做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拭去這份苦惱  就只能做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算失敗再失敗  也只能做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣想的話  就覺得變得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  神田原來是個M啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你說我普通要好很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是櫻花莊的住戶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山現在不也是其中一員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡有目標的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡努力前進的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看誰第一個跑到櫻花莊  我們來比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是最後一個跑的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  沒想到七海竟然沒有帶內褲去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  請你快點忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了流傳給後輩  就將此命名為歡迎七海無內褲花火大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要鬧了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要回想奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意啦  只不過是沒穿內褲奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  No Pants  no Life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說No Pants No Pants了啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺稍微有點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hello  我是從英國來的麗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日式火鍋和壽司很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hey hey look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在模仿社長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想開下機體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
